card.title: The Book of Arralan Season 4: The Greater Good

metadata.author: Morwenna Rose
metadata.description:
Arralan has had some strange visitors arrive, but they are not up to much good and are looking to exploit Arralan.

It’s up to the children to do all they can to stop the place they have come to love from changing forever.
